ZenTask is a modern, intuitive task management application designed to help users organize work, track progress, and stay productive. It supports both authenticated users and guest users, giving a smooth experience even before signing in.

ğŸ§  1. Authentication & Identity
âœ… Guest Mode

Before a user signs in, ZenTask automatically:

Creates a guestId using crypto.randomUUID()

Stores it in localStorage (guestId)

Assigns temporary demo tasks

Persists guest tasks via the API with the x-guest-id header

Benefits:

Zero friction first experience

Users can immediately interact and test

Tasks are preserved until migration

âœ… Sign In / Sign Up

ZenTask supports:

Credential submission via secure API

Automatic migration of guest tasks upon sign-in

Removal of guestId on migration

Persistent user data

Auth State Flags:

authLoading â€” UI loader for network activity

authReady â€” user identity has been determined

isAppHydrating / isAuthStabilizing â€” transition loader while UI catches up

This prevents:

Flash of incorrect UI (hero / task list)

Mid-UX flickers during auth transitions

